# WEKA package metadata for the pwc45 package
PackageName=pwc45
Version=1.1.0
Date=2026-07-04
Title=PWC4.5 - Pairwise Comparative Classification decision tree
Category=Classification
Author=Heba El-Fiqi, Eleni Petraki, Hussein A. Abbass
Maintainer=Heba El-Fiqi <MAINTAINER_EMAIL_TODO>
License=MIT
Description=PWC4.5 is a decision tree algorithm for Pairwise Comparative \
Classification Problems (PWCCP), extending C4.5 to split on the relationship \
between the two members of a pair (numeric relations min/eq/max; nominal \
relations eq/neq) rather than on a value threshold. Input uses the \
pair-as-single-instance representation: p1's n features, then p2's n \
features (same order and types), then the class of p1. Includes C4.5-style \
pessimistic pruning. If you use this package, please cite: H. El-Fiqi, \
E. Petraki, H. A. Abbass, "Pairwise comparative classification for \
translator stylometric analysis", ACM TALLIP 16(1), Article 2, 2016, \
doi:10.1145/2898997.
PackageURL=https://github.com/Hebaelfiqi/PWC4.5/releases
URL=https://github.com/Hebaelfiqi/PWC4.5
Depends=weka (>=3.8.0)
